opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 16th day of October, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the jurist’s name from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
